Section2.Para:
Also in single-fence situation, it is shown that the ACF fences can cut NOx concentration by 30–55 % (Fig. 27.3b). In contrast to the double-fence case, fence with small resistance (




$$ {{\bar{R}}_C}=400 $$

                  ) is better for lowering NOx concentration. In the case of single fence set on the leeside of the road, the lower resistance fence leads to higher pollutant flux into the ACF layer, and thus larger reduction of NOx can be expected.
